<TEXT>&#2;<DATELINE>2006-02-28</DATELINE><TITLE>Steady growth predicted for biocides</TITLE><BODY>Protecting plastics and preventing stain and odour growth have been the main requirements of an antimicrobial. However, consumer perception that products containing biocides can prevent the spread of diseases is also driving growth and prompting new developments with manufacturers. Jennifer Markarian reports.&#3;</BODY></TEXT>